block content
  hero.hero
    .content
      h1 The new standard in online business
      p.
        Hanzo is a data-driven launch pad and platform for modern online businesses.
        Using our AI-powered marketing engine and fintech enabled e-commerce suite, we provide forward-thinking solutions that deliver for your business.

      a.button.docs-button(href="https://dash.hanzo.ai/") START NOW
      a.button(href='https://docs.hanzo.io') CHECK DOCS >

  section.ai-powered
    .content
      h2 Launch and scale data-driven organizations
      p.
        If you can dream it, you can deliver it Hanzo’s AI-powered platform and
        tools saves time and money.  Leverage aggregate data at scale and
        reap the benefits of being apart of our data marketplace.
        Traditional eCommerce Platforms force your business to fit their
        rigidity. Our APIs enable you to deliver sophisticated commerce
        experiences, fully customizable to your business, across every
        digital channel.


    .columns
      .column
        .content
          h3 Collect the right data
          p.
            Hanzo enables you to simplify, streamline, and orchestrate complex
            business logic that is fit-for-purpose to your specific
            requirements.  Full turnkey solution for all data integration,
            collected and utilized in one space.

        .item.content
          h4 Unleash your vision
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-cube.fa-3x
            p.
              Traditional eCommerce platforms masking the underlying complexity
              of their monolith. Hanzo is: Headless with composable
              Microservices, not Headless with a rigid monolithic back-end
        .item.content
          h4 Bring your data to life
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-database.fa-3x
            p.
              We work with you to create a data-and analytics-driven strategy, harness the power of AI to maximize insight-driven opportunities, and build a culture of data democracy to enable and empower users.

      .content
        h3 Use the data
        p.
          When you incorporate big data into improved decision analytics, your company can save time, money and resources while also potentially generating superior results across all relevant fronts.
        .item.content
          h4 Sustainable Success
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-cart-plus.fa-3x
            p.
              Our solutions are designed for the future.  Hanzo provides the necessary infrastructure to fully establish your business online from ecommerce to marketing to shipping and customer support.
        .item.content
          h4 Next-generation Analytics
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-compass.fa-3x
            p.
              Create cost-effective marketing campaigns. Know when and where to grow. Understand the most ideal time to offer a new product or service. Moderate risk while maximizing the return.




  section.support-crypto
    .content
      h2 Our Platform
      p.
        Hanzo's APIs and SDKs provide powerful tools with a flexible commerce API at its core. Whether you're launching a token sale, building a
        marketplace for collectables, or opening an ecommerce store, Hanzo
        enables rapid development of beautiful and secure user experiences.

    .columns
      .column
        .content
          h3 A Complete Solution
          p.
            When it comes to elevating people with the power of data, Hanzo
              combines a laser focus on how people see and understand data with
              the kind of robust, scalable platform you need to run even the
              world’s largest organizations.

        .item.content
          h4 Complete toolkit for online business
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-cubes.fa-3x
            p.
              Whether you’re launching a new crowdfunding campaign, e-commerce
              store, decentralized app or even an asset exchange, Hanzo's
              meticulously designed APIs and SDKs can power your data-driven
              organization.

        .item.content
          h4 Always improving
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-recycle.fa-3x
            p.
              Hanzo is an always-improving toolchain that gains new features
              every month. Our world-class engineering team constantly iterates
              upon every facet of the Hanzo stack.

      .column
        .content
          h3 Global Scale
          p.
            We help power businesss globabally across nearly every industry.
            Headquartered in Los Angeles, Hanzo is working to help transform
            how modern businesses are built and run. Build on a platform
            designed for millions of real-time users.

        .item.content
          h4 Scale to millions of users
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-arrows-alt.fa-3x
            p.
              Enterprise-grade infrastructure that effortlessly handles
              millions of API calls per day. Launch massive campaigns and
              initiatives day one.  Focus on your product and customer
              experience, not developing and operating infrastructure.
        .item.content
          h4 Secure your data
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-lock.fa-3x
            p.
              Be confident your data is secure and trusted. Manage and
              streamline data use with centralized data sources, data
              certification, row-level permissioning, and usage analytics.


  section.developers-first
    .content
      h2 Designed for developers
      p.
        We measure success in how little code you have to write.
        Quickly integrate Hanzo with our well documented SDKs and numerous
        APIs. Our scalable platform is battle-tested and engineered for high
        availability. Hanzo lets you focus on your product and helps you ship
        new features faster.

    .columns
      .column
        .item.content
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-cubes.fa-3x
            p.
              We actively contribute to open-source projects—giving back to the
              community through development, patches, and sponsorships.

        .item.content
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-file-alt.fa-3x
            p.
              World-class <a href='https://docs.hanzo.ai'>documentation,
              libraries, and contracts</a> make building decentralized networks and
              decentralized applications easy.

      .column
        .item.content
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-code-branch.fa-3x
            p.
              Use the tools and workflow you already know and love. Deploy
              smart contracts straight from GitHub and re-deploy whenever you
              push updates.

        .item.content
          .columns
            div
              i.fas.fa-comments.fa-3x
            p.
              Need help? <a href='https://docs.hanzo.ai/discuss'>Ask us anything</a>. Or
              <a href='https://gitter.im/hanzoai/chat'>join us on Gitter</a> and chat
              with our friendly engineers. Need a custom solution? <a
              href="mailto:hi@hanzo.ai">Contact us</a>.
  hero.second-hero
    .content
      h1 Brains + Software
      p.
        Want to supercharge your organization?
        We provide the brains and the software to power your company’s success.
        We have the talent and tools to handle design, marketing, and engineering.
        Hanzo provides essential training and ongoing support to your team as needed.
        Our team of experts is now available to accelerate your success.

      a.button.docs-button(href='mailtojHanzo%20Labs<partner@hanzo.ai>?subject=Partner%20with%20Us') PARTNER WITH HANZO
      a.button.important(href='https://docs.hanzo.ai') LEARN MORE

  a(name='cta')
  cta.get-started.columns
    .content
      h2 READY TO GET STARTED?
    .content
      a.button.docs-button.join-button(href='mailto:hi@hanzo.ai') CONTACT SALES
      a.button.important(href="https://dash.hanzo.ai") START NOW

